            "text": "<p><strong>How To Capture The Photo:</strong></p><ul><li>Take your photo on a smartphone using the camera setting </li><li>If you have a DSLR camera this will be even better, however please make sure you get a good depth of field. </li></ul><p><strong>Lighting:</strong></p><ul><li>We recommend using natural daylight when capturing your photo. </li><li>For photos captured in the evening make sure you have good artificial lighting from </li></ul><p>ceiling lights and lamps etc. </p><p><strong>The Product: </strong></p><ul><li>Make the piece of furniture you’re capturing the focal point of your photo.</li><li>Dress the furniture up with accessories if you have them i.e. cushions, throws. </li><li>Create a realistic homely setting with rugs, coffee tables, lamps etc.</li></ul>",
